                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-2">
                                        Slate.js
                                    </h4>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary m-0">
                                        Uses <strong
                                            >Path-based addressing</strong
                                        >. Nodes can optionally have IDs, but
                                        it's up to the developer to add them.
                                        Most real-world Slate apps add <code
                                            >id</code
                                        > to every Element.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
