                                    <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary m-0">
                                        Uses <strong>ID-based addressing</strong
                                        > with internal <code>__key</code> property
                                        on every node. This is used for React reconciliation
                                        and node lookup. The key is a simple incrementing
                                        integer per editor instance (safe because
                                        it's local, not synced).
                                    </p>
                                </div>
