                                        Uses <strong
                                            >CRDT-based ID addressing</strong
                                        >. Every block has a stable ID that is
                                        used for real-time sync. The underlying
                                        CRDT (Yjs) manages conflict resolution
                                        using Lamport Timestamps embedded in the
                                        ID.
                                    </p>
